										<div class="tags">
																							<a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2019/04/raises-alarm-300-percent-rise-measles-cases-190415162814800.html" target="_blank">Al Jazeera</a>
																								<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/society/2019/apr/15/measles-cases-up-300-worldwide-2019-says-who-vaccination" target="_blank">The Guardian</a>
