								<h2>
																			<a href="https://www.ozy.com/presidential-daily-brief/pdb-93856/in-short-93878/">
											Also Important…										</a>
																		</h2>
								<!--Content-->
								<p>U.S. Democratic presidential candidates <strong><a href="https://apnews.com/6a98a3828317420884341c107462a1ef" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">have raised about $75 million</a></strong> so far this year, with Sen. Bernie Sanders leading the pack with $18 million. Sudan’s main protest group <strong><a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2019/04/sudan-protesters-warn-remnants-bashir-regime-work-190415144622104.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">has warned that “the remnants”</a></strong> of deposed ex-President Omar al-Bashir’s regime threaten the country’s popular revolution. And New Zealand <strong><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/apr/16/new-zealand-suffers-egg-shortage-as-farmers-scramble-to-go-free-range" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">is facing an egg shortage</a></strong> as it transitions to free-range farming and demand for eggs soars.</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://twitter.com/ozyfacts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#OZYfact</a>:</strong> Taking a full year of maternity leave boosted the entrepreneurship of Canadian women by 39 percent compared to male partners and those who took half as much time off. Read more <a href="https://www.ozy.com/acumen/enter-the-era-of-entrepreneur-nity-leave/93635" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">on OZY</a>.</p>
