																								<a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2019/04/15/us/micah-herndon-boston-marathon-crawl-finish-trnd/index.html" target="_blank">CNN</a>
																								<a href="https://www.boston.com/sports/boston-marathon/2019/04/15/this-years-boston-marathon-was-a-tale-of-two-races" target="_blank">Boston</a>
